      "writtenOn": "2019-08-29T18:14:08Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "why is the separate register call needed? Why doesn\u0027t `proto.new_descriptor_set` do this by having `loader\u003dl`? Or is this so that users can have a private descriptor set?\n\nI\u0027m not sure there\u0027s a lot of value in having \u0027private\u0027 protos; At best you\u0027re the only one using them, and at worst folks just load them multiple times into multiple private sets.\n\nUnless I\u0027m misunderstanding?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 41,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 41,
        "endChar": 33
      },
      "revId": "b47b0924da4ce66ee0b12971b5a181c8e8d6e575",
